# forecasting-agent (minimal skeleton)

A tiny end-to-end vertical slice:
- canonical `Event` + `MarketSnapshot`
- local snapshot store (JSON on disk)
- stub feed (deterministic fake data)
- baseline forecaster (use market probability)
- backtest runner + Brier + ECE

## Quickstart

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # Windows: .venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -U pip
pip install -e .
cp .env.example .env
python scripts/run_backtest.py --n-events 30 --n-asofs 5
```

## Notes
- Everything is time-bounded via `as_of` to avoid time-travel.
- Replace `forecasting/feeds/stub.py` with real integrations once the pipeline works.
